name: The Most Beautiful of Mortals: AQUARIUS
description: Ganymedes is so beautiful that even the flirtatious Zeus fell in love with her. He smuggled this beauty to Olympus in the guise of an eagle. Her father was very upset because of the kidnapping. Since the god Zeus would send Ganymedes to earth, various gifts were given to King Tros.Ganymedes draws the attention of all the gods in Olympos.  Zeus too he commissions her to serve as a cupbearer offering wine to the gods.
